Comment: 1,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Comment: 1,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.78,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Did you know, Youko-sama?
Comment: 1,0:03:55.43,0:03:59.53,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Well, if it were based on Sonobe-san,\Nit should be called "Den of Thieves"...
Comment: 1,0:04:35.93,0:04:36.93,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Youko-sama...
Comment: 1,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.93,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Of course Youko-sama wouldn't know!
Comment: 1,0:06:39.48,0:06:45.32,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Please work hard so nasty pests\Ndon't notice Youko-sama.
Comment: 1,0:07:37.71,0:07:41.05,Default,hon,0,0,0,,If you could at least wear\Nsomething like Hayama-san or Futaba-san...
Comment: 1,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.07,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Sonobe-san, {\i1}you{\i0} can wear one{a bikini}.
Comment: 1,0:08:01.93,0:08:04.18,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Curry?! Yakisoba?!
Comment: 1,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.23,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Yuu-san?
Comment: 1,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.93,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Yuu-san?
Comment: 1,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.03,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Teru-chan!
Comment: 1,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.58,Alt,hon,0,0,0,,Yuu-san...
Comment: 1,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.48,Default,hon,0,0,0,,You got tan, Futaba-san.
Comment: 1,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.88,Default,hon,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a Japanese word.
Comment: 1,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.31,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Our "modern Japanese" homework\Nis a reflection essay though.
Comment: 1,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.58,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Will your Japanese be okay?
Comment: 1,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.08,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Yuu-san!
Comment: 1,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.88,Default,hon,0,0,0,,It is all thanks to you, Yuu-san.
Comment: 1,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.21,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, where's Sonobe-san?
Comment: 1,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.38,Alt,hon,0,0,0,,Futaba-chan!
Comment: 1,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.63,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Sakura-san.
Comment: 1,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.13,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Yuu-kun!
Comment: 1,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.82,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Youko-sama, be nice to Yong Master next time.
Comment: 1,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.33,Default,hon,0,0,0,,We will enjoy it in Yuu-san's place, too.
Comment: 1,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.48,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Hayama-san and the others.
Comment: 1,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.63,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Oh, Nishiyama-san.
Comment: 1,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.75,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Oh, Nishiyama-san.
Comment: 1,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.38,Default,hon,0,0,0,,She's just my classmate, Nishiyama-san.
Comment: 1,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.13,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Teru-chan!
Comment: 1,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.13,Alt,hon,0,0,0,,You can do it, Teru-chan!
Comment: 1,0:19:18.98,0:19:21.01,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Come on, Teru-chan.
Comment: 1,0:19:25.48,0:19:28.12,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Hayama-san, you don't like the water?
Comment: 1,0:19:39.58,0:19:40.76,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Hayama-san...
Comment: 1,0:19:40.76,0:19:41.78,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Teru-chan...
Comment: 1,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.13,Default,hon,0,0,0,,Oh, Sonobe-san.
Comment: 1,0:22:01.53,0:22:02.93,Alt,hon,0,0,0,,Youko-sama...
Comment: 1,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.38,Default,sub1,0,0,0,,Hayama-san's sister gave them to me.
Comment: 1,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.73,Default,sub1,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayama-san's sister!
Comment: 1,0:08:33.93,0:08:37.43,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Onee-chan! Onee-chan!
Comment: 1,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.63,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Comment: 1,0:08:47.88,0:08:48.88,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Comment: 1,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.56,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Onee-chan wasn't the one making them?
Comment: 1,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.78,Alt,sub3,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Comment: 1,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.38,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Your onee-sama is very kind.
Comment: 1,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.16,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Comment: 1,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.47,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Well, Onee-chan, let's pla—
Comment: 1,0:18:14.28,0:18:15.38,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Even her ane's here...
Comment: 1,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.83,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Th-That's really Hayama's ane, huh.
Comment: 1,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.38,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Hayama-san's onee-chan gave them to me.
Comment: 1,0:18:11.53,0:18:13.73,Default,sub3,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayama-san's onee-chan!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.93,0:00:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was called "Miso"\Nor "Malt" or something like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.73,0:01:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To keep the nasty pests from staring,\Nwe'll be quick and stealthy.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.73,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.73,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ocean!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.17,0:02:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach is a must during summer!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.37,0:02:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worth waking up early for this.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.98,0:02:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Viewing the ocean from a train\Nlike this is a first for me.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.10,0:02:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, because you're a rich girl, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.33,0:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}was{\i0} one.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At the beach, we've got to...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax on the beach?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sandcastles?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And split a watermelon!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.03,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.48,0:02:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.81,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here to work, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer means the ocean!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean means a beach hut.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough working there as it is...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she has a beach hut version.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.67,0:03:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Always there to serve.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.12,0:03:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the shop is temporarily closed today.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what we were worried about.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.78,0:03:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I've been wondering since earlier...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the name of my shop.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.03,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.95,0:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret Garden...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She would know the name of where she works.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.33,0:03:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought it was called "Miso"\Nor "Malt" or something like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are totally wrong!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a western cake shop!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...or "Shop of Chaos.'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, it's "Himitsu no Hanazono"!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.03,0:04:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Same difference.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite right.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely different!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect for someone\Nwho reeks of the 80's.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.43,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.48,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I get a receipt,\NI cringe with embarrassment.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.25,0:04:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Um, I have a question...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a... "beach hut"?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.68,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.93,0:04:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a rich girl who\Nknows nothing of the world.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have a least {\i1}heard{\i0} of it before!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I just do not know what it is exactly.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain to me what a\Nbeach hut is in plain terms.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.23,0:04:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,With interpretive dance!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Waves.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not understand.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not understand at all.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not think I can work then.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sand! I am sand.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.58,0:05:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a ritual or something?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.08,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, we've come all the way out here...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.26,0:05:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said she would pay us, too...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.33,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose there is no other choice.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go change.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let us.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.63,0:05:53.18,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.63,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully, I didn't approve\Nof this beach hut thing.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing good about getting\Nsunburned and heat stroke.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.23,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To keep the nasty pests from staring...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll be quick and stealthy.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.68,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was playing—
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.43,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? It's so good!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's delicious!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the melon and orange one, too!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but I want to try all of them!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? It sounds good.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try it, too!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious she's a fake customer!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.71,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as usual, I'm forced to help out, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.73,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem dissatisfied.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.45,0:07:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you look different\Nfrom what I had imagined.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.53,0:07:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.98,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I had imagined...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the bright sun!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.68,0:07:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A summer time for girls bursting with youth!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweet lure of a flushed body.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A sweets paradise by the shore!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.58,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Open this summer at the beach hut.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.96,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mwah!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.73,0:07:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-fashioned, as usual.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And you could get sued for\Nthat disguise at the end.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.05,0:07:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not wish to get an unsightly tan.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How about working in a bikini to avoid that?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll make }Like your uniform is a bikini.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is, more like a fancy\Ncafé than a beach hut, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.98,0:07:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.98,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a summer menu with\Ngelato, frappes, and gelatin desserts.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.88,0:08:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What about ramen?!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a dessert shop.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't fried noodles a dessert?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a side dish?!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Open today, Himitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.13,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, the shop's name is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we move somewhere else?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you were\Nworking at a beach hut.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.75,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help with the sales!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have some of everything!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.78,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But the whole menu is\Nice cream and drinks.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Need some help there?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.43,0:09:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not a good idea.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold after eating so much.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not have to push yourself.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.03,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you made this.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.37,Alt,,0,0,0,,Here's the peach {}lassi.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.68,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish it all.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So immature.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really immature.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're an adult doesn't\Nnecessarily mean you're mature.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were aware.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was our pre-opening,\Nso I've closed the shop early.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.28,0:09:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.18,0:09:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We were only open for half the day,\Nbut sales were excellent.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was harder than I expected.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And very hot.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not used to it.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.43,0:10:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a barbecue to restore our\Nenergy since tomorrow will be a full day.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.03,0:10:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat?!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.86,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I want some, too...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,, I'm a man, that much {food }is nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you'll cook the meat for me...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.88,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, the food's ready!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.88,0:10:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't learn.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So immature...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.78,Alt,,0,0,0,,So immature...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.80,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my cooking not to your liking?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.13,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't feel like eating it.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm actually glad...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll have some.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Food is so nourishing after hard work.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grill with the ratio of veggies, meat,\Nmeat, meat, meat, meat, meat, {and }fish!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our profits today...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.88,0:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks so yummy!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You were up early for work today, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to help...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done already.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.93,0:11:26.23,Alt,,0,0,0,,Would you like some, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous since I'm an only child.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.18,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have told me that before!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's the little boy!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to eat any meat?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.58,0:11:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't grow bigger.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make some for you.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be the last straw.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, barbecue should be fine.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.58,0:11:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Raw meat has more vitamins, did you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.73,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call an ambulance, just in case.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the mango frappe.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.48,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our last day working here.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it through, somehow.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.04,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't get to play at all,\Neven though we're at the beach...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been working this whole time.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.75,0:12:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both for accompanying me this whole time.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,More like burnt.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's summer!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.58,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer means curry!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.23,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't I kind of like curry?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.13,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have a farmer's tan now,\Nso I want to even it out.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.29,0:12:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be done working, so let's\Ngo all out and play tomorrow!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.06,0:13:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't gone into the ocean\Nso we need to take this chance now!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.93,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty much done with homework\Nso let's have fun for the rest of summer.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Homewor—?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.06,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.93,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will prepare lunch for you as thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any requests?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbecue!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We had that the first day.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the beach without barbecue?!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to the beach than that!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How about curry?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough just looking at you.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave it up to me, then.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, let us enjoy the beach tomorrow!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.83,0:13:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The ocean is plentiful.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to catch stuff?!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.93,Alt,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make the most out of tomorrow!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.43,0:14:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the species, freshness,\Nand cooking preparation.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aw, man}Geez!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.43,Alt,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.23,Alt,,0,0,0,,I can't swim!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.63,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been nice if it were\Na dolphin rather than a shark.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not working today, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can play, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we thought...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a shark—
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.98,0:14:28.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought tickets for the hotel pool.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's go here!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can we?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we barbecue there?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it was a hotel.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A pool!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.53,0:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's been a while since I've\Ngone to a pool with you.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.84,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, make sure to stretch.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a floatie.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you came with your mom.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The lunches are taking longer than expected.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she would meet us by lunch.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to come here with my family.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.53,0:15:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably emotional\Ndamage rather than physical.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I should.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.44,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's enjoy this pool!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is amazing!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hotel pools are great!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your swimsuit is pretty amazing too, though.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is normal!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.33,0:16:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, it's amazing you\Ngot free tickets for this pool.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone gave them to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Really}Gave them?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so heavy!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can help you.}Do you need some help?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.13,0:17:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, she gave me the tickets she won.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.73,0:17:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really enjoy myself now that I know.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.23,0:17:23.08,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're totally enjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ignore them... ignore...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.38,0:17:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're totally enjoying themselves...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.93,Alt,,0,0,0,,I-Ignore them.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.38,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Got some turban shells!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.13,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm practicing catching\Nsea urchin or abalone and stuff.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that here!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.88,0:17:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.83,0:17:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's against the law unless\Nyou're a fisherman.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are—
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.75,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always follow me?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, do you {\i1}like{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.58,Alt,,0,0,0,,Don't make up gross things like that!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the nice girl from before.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.38,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she your friend, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.13,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're all here let's all play together!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai—
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.30,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have some friends here...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll go finish my sandcastle—
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should swim, too!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You should know. I can't—
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you can't swim, huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.63,0:18:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty scary if something happens, huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, if your boat sinks in\Nthe middle of the ocean.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.13,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's practice swimming!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.46,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In case you really need to some day.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I really need to...?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.94,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.73,0:19:04.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,Like now?!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to try harder.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way, no way!{ I can't!}
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.12,0:19:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about liking or not,\NI just can't swim.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lasted this long not\Nknowing how to swim.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine just the way I am.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.53,0:19:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go practice in the kiddie pool.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.83,Alt,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.68,Alt,,0,0,0,,Please try your best.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.88,0:19:54.93,Alt,,0,0,0,,Everyone! I brought lunch.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saved.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You took a while.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.28,0:20:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it took me longer since there\Nwere so many unfamiliar things.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your lunch.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really took a while since\Nit was a first for me, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.53,0:20:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, why are you both beat up?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.03,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just harder than expected.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.13,0:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was wild.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.76,0:20:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we got a hold of a rare ingredient.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rare ingredient?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.13,0:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the shark will be\Nbothering us anymore,
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still don't recommend swimming\Nsince there are many jellyfish.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, is that so?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.78,0:20:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Delish!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You ate it?!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ground meat.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem like good friends.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You do get sleepy after swimming.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.28,0:21:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use me as a pillow, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, you can lean on me.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.83,0:21:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That would be improper.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't eat another bite.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She would...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.48,Alt,,0,0,0,,Was she sleep talking?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.03,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably having a feast\Nin her dream right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.28,0:21:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have a feast if I sleep?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.18,0:21:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.48,0:21:53.08,Alt,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep. Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.58,0:21:55.93,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sleep. Sleep.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.48,0:21:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can sleep\Nif you try that hard.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.93,0:21:59.33,Alt,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep. Sleep.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.03,0:22:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep. Sleep.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.28,0:22:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.23,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep. Go to sleep...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Sonobe Shino.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.35,0:22:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Nishikawa Family's former maid.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.05,0:22:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.35,0:22:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Their "to each their own color" life is so entertaining.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.95,0:22:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.25,0:22:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.43,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This August, I present Himitsu no\NHanazono, beach hut version!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsugu found this suitable place for me.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaji...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.88,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...{but }what's "Himitsu no Hanazono"?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...is English for "Himitsu no Hanazono"!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yamaji.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew, Yamaji?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.03,0:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, from today we'll be Himitsu\Nno Hanazono, beach hut version!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.86,0:04:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonobe!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Himitsu no Hanazono.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Himitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.38,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Beach hut, Himitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaji!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.93,0:12:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Beach hut, Himitsu no Hanazono!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Usuda. Why are you here?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not good at dealing with Sakura.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sakura went with him.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's so {cool}amazing, Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was Hayama's...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like Hayama is here.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.78,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Did you know, Miss Youko?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.43,0:03:59.53,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Well, if it were based on Miss Sonobe,\Nit should be called "Den of Thieves"...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.93,0:04:36.93,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Miss Youko...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.93,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Of course Miss Youko wouldn't know!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.48,0:06:45.32,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Please work hard so nasty pests\Ndon't notice Miss Youko.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.71,0:07:41.05,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,If you could at least wear\Nsomething like Hayama or Futaba...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.07,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Miss Sonobe, {\i1}you{\i0} can wear one{a bikini}.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.93,0:08:04.18,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Curry?! Fried noodles?!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.23,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Yuu?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.93,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Yuu?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.03,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.58,Alt,no hon,0,0,0,,Yuu...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.48,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,You got tan, Futaba.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.06,0:13:10.88,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I know that word.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.31,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Our modern Japanese homework is a reflection essay.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.58,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.08,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.88,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,It is all thanks to you, Yuu.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.28,0:15:07.21,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, where's Miss Sonobe?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.38,Alt,no hon,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.63,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.13,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.82,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Miss Youko, be nice to Yong Master next time.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.33,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,We will enjoy it in Yuu's place, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.48,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Hayama and the others.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.63,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Oh, Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.75,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Oh, Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.38,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,She's just my classmate, Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.13,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.13,Alt,no hon,0,0,0,,You can do it, Teru!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.98,0:19:21.01,Default,no hon,0,0,0,,Come on, Teru.
